/*------------------------------------------------------------------
 MBlue Mercury Skin (Ver. 0.2.0)

Author: M.BLUE - Tested on: Firefox 3.5.0 - Last Update: 15.12.2009
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Description:
1. Transforms the Menu-bar, Nav-bar, Bookmarks-bar and the Tabs.
2. Transforms the Menu-Bar Menus into a FF logo (orb). Hovering the
   logo shows the menus.
3. Makes the Menu-Bar Menus Iconic.
4. Moves the Tabs to the top (like Chrome).
5. Supports "Faviconize Tab" Ext.
6. Customizable. SCROLL DOWN TO CUSTOMIZE!!

Notes:
-If something looks wrong, make sure you aren't using other
 styles/extensions that changes the Toolbars/Tabs settings. And use
 the default Firefox theme.
--------------------------------------------------------------------
CUSTOMIZING:
1. TOOLBARS PADDING.
2. TOOLBARS BACKGROUND-COLOR/BORDER.
3. TAB TEXT SETTINGS.
4. LOGO OPACITY/ALWAYS VISIBLE.

> SCROLL DOWN TO CUSTOMIZE!!
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Supported Extensions:
Faviconize Tab.

--------------------------------------------------------------------
Updates:
15.12.2009 Ver. 0.2.0 = done?
19.07.2009 Ver. 0.1.9 = added FF 3.5 shadow support
07.05.2009 Ver. 0.1.6 = almost ready to release
14.02.2009 Ver. 0.1.5 = lot of fixes, added custom options
14.11.2008 Ver. 0.1.0 = temp version
------------------------------------------------------------------*/



